      <title>石墨矿商游说美国政府对中国采购的电动汽车材料征税</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/graphite-miners-lobby-us-govt-impose-levy-china-sourced-ev-material-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北美石墨矿商正在游说美国政府对来自中国的三种石墨产品征收 25% 的关税，以对抗北京对汽车电池关键材料的垄断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/graphite-miners-lobby-us-govt-impose-levy-china-sourced-ev-material-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:35:14 GMT</pubDate>
